  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PROTIP:</strong> always find an exit first before doing your looting spree.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/bb6e2da95108bb83d891e875df0d5f13.poster.avif?t=1763058240\" width=650 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/bb6e2da95108bb83d891e875df0d5f13.webm?t=1763058240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/e1a7d3c1dfe1b3a220536d69d4fa1506.webp?t=1763058240\" width=650 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you ever wanted to feel like a military commander, now is your chance.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roguelike elements: achievements with rewards on new games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Management of resources</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Event system with 4 polls for each day (night camp, morning event, strategic choices and tactical deployment)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Squad-based real-time tactics combat (with an optional active pause mode) / Real Time Strategy </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unit customization (Level up skills mechanics, Equipment upgrades)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/5532bf52c9abfa90b56b2f45fc1e8c82.avif?t=1763058240\" width=652 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/3c25c6e424832d8a02d2672b3dafc717.webp?t=1763058240\" width=650 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious deadly plague has infected the city of Sun Stone, and all communications with the city administration have been cut off.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the appointed commander who must assemble a strike team and deploy them within the epicenter to find answers before the plague spreads beyond the city limits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/ac98314339248f765fa1a09aade7b0ae.avif?t=1763058240\" width=650 height=208 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will get to make strategic decisions that will impact the status, supplies, and sanity of your squad, and tactical decisions that will impact the survival chances of your strike team during combat engagement with the creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The lives of your men are in your hands and the story will be shaped according to your choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/32ca7144cffb075567c05eaf3a4f9dc9.webp?t=1763058240\" width=650 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is rather short but emphasizes the replayability factor making each playthrough as unique and fresh as possible by giving you different new games</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >bonus options, a bit of randomly generated content, achievements with rewards on the next game, multiple strategic choices with various outcomes, multiple paths, multiple endings and multiple ways to play.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/caf8a8f417443ff862a79307d552a82f.poster.avif?t=1763058240\" width=650 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/caf8a8f417443ff862a79307d552a82f.webm?t=1763058240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fair Warning: the game can become very hard if you get too greedy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/fc4d1d5d42ccbb89b0842402f49a2064.webp?t=1763058240\" width=650 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game contains 5 chapters represented by the 5 stages of DEFCON:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEFCON 5  -</strong> the initial stage of the outbreak, the first contact of the strike team with the quarantine city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEFCON 4 -</strong> things spice up, new types of infected appear, maps become bigger, and event pools refresh.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEFCON 3 -</strong> here there will be all Bosses encounters. Think outside the box.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEFCON 2 -</strong> all you learned so far and more, maps become bigger, all stakes are amplified, and difficulty is  increased.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEFCON 1 -</strong> all choices you made so far in the game since the beginning will now have a direct impact on the gameplay and on the ending cutscene.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each difficulty setting has its unique layout in how many days each DEFCON has.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/ef5b1074b6119305309f857634e421e0.webp?t=1763058240\" width=650 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game has a Lovecraftian - Military theme, mixing Real-time strategy gameplay with heavy Horror elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/265225c717988e94b76b95ca6e708364.avif?t=1763058240\" width=650 height=429 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                        Good luck Commander! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PROTIP:</strong> always find an exit first before doing your looting spree.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/bb6e2da95108bb83d891e875df0d5f13.poster.avif?t=1763058240\" width=650 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/bb6e2da95108bb83d891e875df0d5f13.webm?t=1763058240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/e1a7d3c1dfe1b3a220536d69d4fa1506.webp?t=1763058240\" width=650 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you ever wanted to feel like a military commander, now is your chance.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roguelike elements: achievements with rewards on new games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Management of resources</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Event system with 4 polls for each day (night camp, morning event, strategic choices and tactical deployment)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Squad-based real-time tactics combat (with an optional active pause mode) / Real Time Strategy </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unit customization (Level up skills mechanics, Equipment upgrades)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/5532bf52c9abfa90b56b2f45fc1e8c82.avif?t=1763058240\" width=652 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ct