d multiple ways to play.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/caf8a8f417443ff862a79307d552a82f.poster.avif?t=1763058240\" width=650 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/caf8a8f417443ff862a79307d552a82f.webm?t=1763058240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fair Warning: the game can become very hard if you get too greedy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/fc4d1d5d42ccbb89b0842402f49a2064.webp?t=1763058240\" width=650 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game contains 5 chapters represented by the 5 stages of DEFCON:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEFCON 5  -</strong> the initial stage of the outbreak, the first contact of the strike team with the quarantine city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEFCON 4 -</strong> things spice up, new types of infected appear, maps become bigger, and event pools refresh.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEFCON 3 -</strong> here there will be all Bosses encounters. Think outside the box.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEFCON 2 -</strong> all you learned so far and more, maps become bigger, all stakes are amplified, and difficulty is  increased.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEFCON 1 -</strong> all choices you made so far in the game since the beginning will now have a direct impact on the gameplay and on the ending cutscene.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each difficulty setting has its unique layout in how many days each DEFCON has.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/ef5b1074b6119305309f857634e421e0.webp?t=1763058240\" width=650 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game has a Lovecraftian - Military theme, mixing Real-time strategy gameplay with heavy Horror elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/265225c717988e94b76b95ca6e708364.avif?t=1763058240\" width=650 height=429 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                        Good luck Commander! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
